// 根据 HAR entries.startedDateTime 校验存档日期（优先使用 entries 最大 startedDateTime 对应日期，无法解析时回退到“出现次数最多的日期”）
function validateDateAgainstStartedDateTime(chosenDate, rawText, options){
  const opts = options || {};
  const follow = document.getElementById('followTextDate')?.checked;
  if(!rawText || !rawText.trim()) return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: '' };
  const strategy = opts.strategy || 'max';
  if(strategy === 'latest_for_day'){
    // 仅用于当日校准：不跨天，若文本最大日期不等于所选日期，则保留所选日期
    const latest = detectLatestDateFromText(rawText);
    if(!latest) return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: 'no_detected' };
    if(chosenDate && latest !== chosenDate){
      return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: 'keep_today' };
    }
    return { date: chosenDate || latest, changed: !chosenDate, reason: chosenDate ? '' : 'empty_chosen' };
  }
  const detected = strategy === 'earliest' ? detectEarliestDateFromText(rawText)
                   : strategy === 'latest' ? detectLatestDateFromText(rawText)
                   : detectDateFromText(rawText);
  if(!detected) return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: 'no_detected' };
  if(!chosenDate){
    return { date: detected, changed: true, reason: 'empty_chosen' };
  }
  if(chosenDate !== detected){
    if(follow || opts.enforce){
      return { date: detected, changed: true, reason: 'mismatch_follow' };
    } else {
      showError(`所选日期(${chosenDate})与文本中的 startedDateTime(${detected})不一致，请确认或开启“跟随文本日期”`);
      return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: 'mismatch' };
    }
  }
  return { date: chosenDate, changed: false, reason: '' };
}

